trainers.name: Worker Jason
trainers.dialogue: Hope you've bundled up! It's a long trek to the town!

trainers.name: Bounty Hunter Candace
trainers.dialogue: Tracks in the snow don’t lie. You’re next.

trainers.name: Black Belt Oliver
trainers.dialogue: I constantly train to keep warm in the snow.

trainers.name: Boarder Noah
trainers.dialogue: The snow’s packed tight, and so is my team!

trainers.name: Skier Ursula
trainers.dialogue: If you can’t keep up, you’ll get left in the snow.

trainers.name: Boarder Terry
trainers.dialogue: Snowboards aren’t just for tricks; they’re for taking down opponents!

trainers.name: Skier Mark
trainers.dialogue: Most people don't appreciate the colder climate.

trainers.name: Skier Sherry
trainers.dialogue: You never really get used to the weather.
